    <mxCell id="18" value="<b>Robot: Unitree G1</b><br>ArticulationCfg (URDF→USD)<br>39 bodies, 29 DOF<br>activate_contact_sensors=True<br>Stiffness=0, Damping=0<br>(Manual PD torque control)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="17">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="36" width="345" height="120" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="19" value="<b>Ball: RigidObject</b><br>SphereCfg (radius=0.11m)<br>mass=0.6 kg<br>Aerodynamic drag applied<br>Respawned every ball_interval_s=0.5s<br>max_ball_vel=0.5 m/s" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="17">
      <mxGeometry x="375" y="36" width="345" height="120" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="20" value="<b>ContactSensor</b><br>prim_path: .*/Robot/.*<br>net_forces_w (world frame)<br>Feet: left/right_ankle_roll_link<br>Hands: left/right_rubber_hand<br>Knees: left/right_knee_link" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="17">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="168" width="345" height="120" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="21" value="<b>Ground + Scene</b><br>Static flat plane<br>spacing=5.0m between envs<br>replicate_physics=True<br>512 envs in grid layout" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="17">
      <mxGeometry x="375" y="168" width="345" height="120" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="22" value="<b>6 Ball Target Regions</b><br>0: Right mid  h[0.4-1.2] w[0.2-1.2]<br>1: Left mid   h[0.4-1.2] w[-1.2-(-0.2)]<br>2: Right high h[1.2-1.6] w[0.0-1.0]<br>3: Left high  h[1.2-1.6] w[-1.0-0.0]<br>4: Right low  h[0.1-0.3] w[0.2-1.2]<br>5: Left low   h[0.1-0.3] w[-1.2-(-0.2)]" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="17">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="300" width="702" height="140" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="23" value="<b>Ball Visibility Mask (flying):</b>  ball_x∈[0.05,3.4], ball_y∈[-2,2], ball_z&lt;1.8, catchstep&gt;0, approaching<br><b>random_vanish:</b> ball obs zeroed after vanish_step — trains robot to act without late-stage ball info" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="17">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="452" width="702" height="80" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="24" value="<b>Ball Drag:</b>  F_drag = -0.5 × ρ × Cd × A × v² × v̂   applied each physics step" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="17">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="544" width="702" height="60" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="25" value="<b>Control Step Loop</b>" style="swimlane;startSize=28;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="770" y="270" width="950" height="640" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="26" value="<b>Timing:</b>  physics dt=5ms (200Hz)  |  policy dt=20ms (50Hz)  |  decimation=4" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="25">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="36" width="910" height="36" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="27" value="<b>1. _pre_physics_step()</b><br>• Clip actions to [-100, 100]<br>• Build delayed_actions [4, N, 29]<br>• d ~ Uniform(0,4)  per env<br>• a_delayed[i] = a_old + (a_new−a_old)×(i≥d)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="25">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="82" width="450" height="115" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="28" value="<b>2. _apply_action() ×4</b><br>• Select delayed_actions[substep]<br>• ε ~ U(−0.01,0.01)×τ_lim  (inject)<br>• τ = Kp·fp·(θt−θ) − Kd·fd·θ̇ + bias + ε<br>• Clip τ to torque_limits<br>• Ball drag force applied" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="25">
      <mxGeometry x="480" y="82" width="450" height="115" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="29" value="<b>3. _get_dones()</b><br>Termination if ANY true:<br>• knee_z &lt; 0.10 m<br>• |gravity_tilt_xy| &gt; 0.8<br>• Sharp foot contact force<br>Timeout: max_episode_length_s" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="25">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="207" width="450" height="120" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="30" value="<b>4. _get_observations()</b><br>• _update_ball_target()<br>• _randomize_balls()<br>• _push_robots() every 15s<br>• Build 96-dim frame obs<br>• Roll actor_history_buf" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="25">
      <mxGeometry x="480" y="207" width="450" height="120" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="31" value="<b>5. _compute_rewards()</b><br>Sum of 22 components<br>(see rewards panel →)<br>Curriculum: stopball scale<br>grows with success rate" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="25">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="337" width="450" height="100" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="32" value="<b>6. _reset_idx()</b>  (if done)<br>• _reset_dofs() + pose rand<br>• Resample Kp,Kd,bias<br>• New ball trajectory<br>• Clear history/action buffs" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="25">
      <mxGeometry x="480" y="337" width="450" height="100" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="33" value="<b>Curriculum:</b>  Every 500 steps → expand command ranges by 0.3×avg_success.  rew_stopball = stop_init×(1+0.5×curriculum)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="25">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="447" width="910" height="50" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="34" value="<b>Push Robots:</b>  every push_interval=15s  |  vel_impulse ~ U(−1.5,1.5) m/s XY  |  simulates external disturbances" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=10;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="25">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="507" width="910" height="50" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="35" value="<b>Observation Space</b>" style="swimlane;startSize=28;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="1730" y="270" width="2440" height="640" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="36" value="<b>POLICY OBS: 960-dim [N, 960]</b> = 10 history frames × 96-dim/frame" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="36" width="1400" height="40" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="37" value="<b>ball_local [3]</b><br>= quat_apply_inv(root_q, ball_pos−torso)<br>× flying_mask × vanish_mask<br>scale=0.3, noise σ=0.08" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="86" width="340" height="100" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="38" value="<b>ang_vel [3]</b><br>= base_ang_vel_w × 0.25<br>noise σ=0.2 rad/s" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="368" y="86" width="220" height="100" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="39" value="<b>projected_gravity [3]</b><br>= quat_apply_inv(base_q,[0,0,−1])<br>measures body tilt, noise σ=0.05" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="598" y="86" width="280" height="100" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="40" value="<b>dof_pos [29]</b><br>= (joint_pos−default)×1.0<br>noise σ=0.01 rad" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="888" y="86" width="230" height="100" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="41" value="<b>dof_vel [29]</b><br>= joint_vel×0.05<br>noise σ=1.5 rad/s" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="1128" y="86" width="230" height="100" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="42" value="<b>actions [29]</b><br>= last_actions<br>(no noise)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="1368" y="86" width="200" height="100" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="43" value="<b>Frame total: 3+3+3+29+29+29 = 96 dim</b>   ×   <b>10 history frames</b>   =   <b>960-dim policy obs</b>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="196" width="1550" height="36" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="44" value="<b>History buffer actor_history_buf [N, 960]:</b><br>obs[:,0:96]=oldest frame … obs[:,864:960]=newest (t)  |  rolled each step, reset on episode end" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="242" width="1550" height="60" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="45" value="<b>CRITIC (PRIVILEGED) OBS: 113-dim [N, 113]</b>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="1588" y="36" width="820" height="40" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="46" value="<b>Privileged components:</b><br>base_lin_vel [3]<br>base_ang_vel [3]<br>projected_gravity [3]<br>ball_local [3]<br>ball_vel_world [3]<br>hand_pos_left [3]<br>hand_pos_right [3]<br>dof_pos [29]<br>dof_vel [29]<br>actions [29]<br>end_target [3]<br>──────────────<br>Total: 113 dim" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="1588" y="86" width="380" height="220" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="47" value="⚠ <b>Quaternion Convention</b><br>Isaac Lab: <b>wxyz</b> (≠ xyzw Isaac Gym)<br>Use: quat_apply_inverse()<br>NOT: quat_rotate_inverse()<br><br><b>Joint Order</b><br>Isaac Lab: breadth-first<br>Use find_joints() not hardcoded idx" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="1988" y="86" width="380" height="220" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="48" value="<b>AMP Motion Observation (DISCONNECTED ⚠):</b><br>58-dim = [dof_pos_t(29), dof_pos_t−1(29)]<br>MotionLib loads 60 motion clips from datasets/goalkeeper/*.pt<br>AMP discriminator coef=0.4 — NOT connected to PPO loss in rsl_rl 3.x<br>Result: standard PPO only; motion naturalness not enforced during training" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="316" width="2390" height="80" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="49" value="<b>clip_observations=100  |  add_noise=True  |  noise_level=1.0</b><br>Ball visibility: flying=(x∈[0.05,3.4])∧(y∈[−2,2])∧(z&lt;1.8)∧approaching  |  random_vanish=step&gt;vanish_step" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="35">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="406" width="2390" height="60" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="50" value="<b>Domain Randomization  (Direct Workflow — inline in env methods)</b>" style="swimlane;startSize=28;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="10" y="930" width="1120" height="660" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="51" value="<b># | Parameter | Range | When | Why</b>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=10;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="36" width="1082" height="28" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="52" value="<b>1. Joint Injection</b>  ±0.01 rad × τ_lim<br>Every step (_apply_action)<br><i>Sensor noise on commanded angles</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="72" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="53" value="<b>2. Actuation Offset</b>  ±0.01 × τ_lim<br>Each reset (_reset_idx)<br><i>Systematic motor bias/friction</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0eaf5;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="124" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="54" value="<b>3. Payload Mass</b>  −5 to +10 kg<br>Init + reset<br><i>Variable load (ball, tools)</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="176" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="55" value="<b>4. CoM Displacement</b>  ±0.10 m per axis<br>Init + reset<br><i>Manufacturing asymmetry, wear</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0eaf5;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="228" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="56" value="<b>5. Link Mass Scale</b>  ×[0.8, 1.2]<br>Init + reset<br><i>Component tolerance variation</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="280" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="57" value="<b>6. Friction Coeff ⚠</b>  [0.1, 2.0]<br>Each reset (NOT applied*)<br><i>Ground grip variation</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0eaf5;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="332" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="58" value="<b>7. Restitution ⚠</b>  [0.0, 1.0]<br>Each reset (NOT applied*)<br><i>Ball bounce variation</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="384" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="59" value="<b>8. Kp Position Gain</b>  ×[0.8, 1.2]<br>Each reset (_reset_idx)<br><i>Servo stiffness uncertainty</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0eaf5;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="436" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="60" value="<b>9. Kd Velocity Gain</b>  ×[0.8, 1.2]<br>Each reset (_reset_idx)<br><i>Servo damping uncertainty</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="488" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="61" value="<b>10. Initial Joint Pos</b>  off±0.1r scale[0.5-1.5]<br>Each reset (_reset_dofs)<br><i>Episode start variation</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0eaf5;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="540" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="62" value="<b>11. Control Delay</b>  [0,4] steps=0−20ms<br>Every step (_pre_physics)<br><i>Network/actuator latency</i>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="592" width="1082" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="63" value="⚠ Friction/Restitution: buffers allocated but write_physics_material_properties_to_sim() never called → silently no-op" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=9;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="50">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="644" width="1082" height="32" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="64" value="<b>Action Space + PD Control</b>" style="swimlane;startSize=28;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="1140" y="930" width="1110" height="660" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="65" value="<b>Action Space: 29-dim continuous  [N, 29]</b><br>Each dim = target joint angle offset (normalized)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="64">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="36" width="1072" height="48" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="66" value="<b>Action Pipeline:</b><br>1. Policy outputs a ∈ [−1, 1]^29<br>2. Scale: θ_target = default_pos + a × action_scale<br>3. Clip: θ_target clamped to joint_pos_limits<br>4. Delay: apply delayed_actions[substep]<br>5. Inject: add joint_injection noise ε" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="64">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="94" width="520" height="160" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="67" value="<b>PD Control Formula:</b><br><br>τ = Kp · f_p · (θ_target − θ_actual)<br>  − Kd · f_d · θ̇_actual<br>  + bias  (actuation_offset)<br>  + ε    (joint_injection)<br><br>τ_clipped = clamp(τ, −τ_lim, +τ_lim)<br><br>set_joint_effort_target(τ_clipped)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="64">
      <mxGeometry x="558" y="94" width="534" height="160" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="68" value="<b>Gain Factors (per DOF, per env):</b><br>f_p = Kp_factors[env, dof]  ~ U(0.8, 1.2)  ← resampled each episode<br>f_d = Kd_factors[env, dof]  ~ U(0.8, 1.2)  ← resampled each episode<br>bias = actuation_offset[env,dof] ~ U(−0.01,0.01)×τ_lim  ← resampled each episode<br>ε    = joint_injection[env,dof]  ~ U(−0.01,0.01)×τ_lim  ← resampled EVERY STEP" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="64">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="264" width="1072" height="100" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="69" value="<b>29 DOF Joints (G1):</b><br>Left leg (6): hip_pitch, hip_roll, hip_yaw, knee, ankle_pitch, ankle_roll<br>Right leg (6): same structure<br>Waist (3): yaw, roll, pitch<br>Left arm (7): shoulder_pitch/roll/yaw, elbow, wrist_roll/pitch/yaw<br>Right arm (7): same structure<br>clip_actions=100  |  torque_limits per-joint from URDF" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="64">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="374" width="1072" height="130" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="70" value="<b>Delay Detail:</b>  d ~ Uniform(0,4) steps per env per step<br>a_delayed[i] = a_prev + (a_curr − a_prev) × float(i ≥ d)<br>i=0: earliest substep  |  i=3: latest substep  |  d=0 → no delay  |  d=4 → full 20ms lag" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="64">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="514" width="1072" height="80" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="71" value="<b>clip_actions=100</b>  |  <b>stiffness=damping=0</b> in Isaac Lab config (manual PD only)  |  Torques applied via set_joint_effort_target()" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=9;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="64">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="604" width="1072" height="36" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
