    <mxCell id="100" value="<b>Total reward = Σ(scale × component)  |  only_positive_rewards=False  |  clip_observations=100</b><br>Curriculum: stopball_scale = stop_init × (1 + 0.5 × curriculum_update)  where curriculum = avg_ep_len/50" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=9;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="72">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="458" width="1880" height="60" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="101" value="<b>Termination thresholds:</b>  knee_z&lt;0.10m  |  gravity_tilt&gt;0.8  |  sharp_contact_at_feet<br><b>Episode reset:</b>  max_episode_length_s exceeded (timeout, no penalty)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=9;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="72">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="528" width="1880" height="56" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="102" value="<b>Success criteria:</b>  dist(hand,target)&lt;reach_th=0.2m  AND  hand_height&gt;handheight_th=1.0m  AND  ball_stopped  AND  ball_in_zone<br><b>catch_th=0.5  |  strict_th=0.15  |  catch_sigma=5.0  |  target_dof_pos_sigma=−20</b>" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=9;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="72">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="592" width="1880" height="56" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="103" value="<b>AMP Motion Priors (HIM-PPO) — NOT CONNECTED in Isaac Lab port</b>" style="swimlane;startSize=28;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#b85450;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="10" y="1610" width="2220" height="360" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="104" value="<b>Original Architecture (Isaac Gym):</b><br>HimPPO extends PPO with adversarial motion discriminator<br>Discriminator input: 58-dim (dof_pos_t + dof_pos_t−1)<br>Discriminator output: motion naturalness score<br>AMP gradient: amp_coef=0.4 × discriminator_loss added to PPO loss<br>Effect: policy learns both task AND natural motion simultaneously" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="103">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="36" width="1060" height="200" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="105" value="<b>Motion Dataset:</b><br>Location: legged_gym/resources/datasets/goalkeeper/*.pt<br>60 motion clips loaded via MotionLib<br>Frame rate: 30 fps  |  min_time=0.1s<br>obs_type='dof'  |  num_obs=58 (29+29)<br>Used as: reference distribution for discriminator" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="103">
      <mxGeometry x="1088" y="36" width="1110" height="200" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="106" value="<b>Status in Isaac Lab port:</b>  MotionLib loads 60 clips successfully  |  58-dim AMP obs computed each step<br>BUT: rsl_rl 3.x OnPolicyRunner uses standard PPO only — no discriminator, no AMP gradient<br><b>Impact:</b> Policy learns task rewards but NOT motion naturalness → may be jerky on hardware<br><b>Fix needed:</b> Reimplement HIM-PPO or use Isaac Lab's native AMP runner (~20h effort)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=center;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="103">
      <mxGeometry x="18" y="248" width="2180" height="96" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="107" value="<b>Available Commands / Config</b>" style="swimlane;startSize=28;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="2240" y="1610" width="1850" height="360" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="108" value="<b>Training Commands:</b><br># Smoke test (16 envs, 50 steps)<br>python -u scripts/test_env.py --headless --num_envs=16 --steps=50<br><br># Headless training (512 envs)<br>python -u scripts/train.py --headless --num_envs=512 --max_iterations=200000<br><br># RTX 5090 (2048 envs)<br>python -u scripts/train.py --headless --num_envs=2048 --max_iterations=200000<br><br># RTX 5090 max scale (4096 envs)<br>python -u scripts/train.py --headless --num_envs=4096 --max_iterations=200000<br><br># With GUI (2 envs)<br>python -u scripts/train.py --num_envs=2 --max_iterations=200000" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="107">
