    <mxCell id="109" value="<b>Key Config Flags (GoalkeeperEnvCfg):</b><br>delay=True  |  decimation=4  |  num_envs=512<br>push_robots=True  |  push_interval_s=15<br>ball_interval_s=0.5  |  max_ball_vel=0.5<br>add_noise=True  |  noise_level=1.0<br>clip_actions=100  |  clip_obs=100<br><br><b>Domain rand flags (all True):</b><br>randomize_joint_injection  |  kp  |  kd<br>actuation_offset  |  payload_mass<br>com_displacement  |  link_mass<br>friction  |  restitution  |  initial_joint_pos<br><br><b>Env:</b>  conda activate env_isaaclab<br><b>Logs:</b>  logs/rsl_rl/goalkeeper/<br><b>Python:</b>  always use python -u (unbuffered)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" edge="0" parent="107">
